  20 Oct 2006; Gustavo Zacarias <gustavoz@gentoo.org>
  audacious-1.1.2-r1.ebuild:
  Stable on sparc

  20 Oct 2006; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> audacious-1.1.2-r1.ebuild:
  Marked 1.1.2-r1 stable on x86.

*audacious-1.2.0_rc3 (12 Oct 2006)

  12 Oct 2006; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> -audacious-1.2.0_rc2.ebuild,
  +audacious-1.2.0_rc3.ebuild:
  Update due to regression; the new skinning engine was not fully compatible
  with old skins. The title will now display correctly on old-style skins.

*audacious-1.2.0_rc2 (12 Oct 2006)

  12 Oct 2006; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> +audacious-1.2.0_rc2.ebuild:
  New release candidate. Improved skinning engine (freeform skins now
  supported), see the included Osmosis skin for a demonstration. Bugfixes &
  stability improvements, as usual.

  11 Oct 2006; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> audacious-1.2.0_rc1.ebuild:
  Add taglib dependency (which will not be in 1.2 final; the configure script
  is wrong on this), closes bug #148729.

*audacious-1.2.0_rc1 (18 Sep 2006)

